-- ===================================================================================
-- Author        : System
-- Created date  : 18 Mar 2016 00:14:36
-- Description   : Provide function to retrieve [dbo].[ClosingPeriod] data.
--
-- NOTE: This Function is initially generated by system and can be modified following
